      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 20.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 20.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>絕學無憂，唯之與阿，相去幾何？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When we renounce learning we have no troubles.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-020__align-002">
