      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 20.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>眾人熙熙，如享太牢，如春登臺。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What space the gulf between shall fill?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
