      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 20.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我獨泊兮其未兆，如嬰兒之未孩；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What all men fear is indeed to be feared; but how wide and without end is the range of questions (asking to be discussed)!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
