      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 20.19</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>我獨異於人，而貴食母。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>(Thus) I alone am different from other men, but I value the nursing-mother (the Dao).</seg>
      </tuv>
